metadata.name: Non-Fungible Dreams
metadata.description:
Many of us, who are the frontiers in Web3 evolution, have been there. Some of us are still in here in this dream state of consciousness. 

We dream about NFTs, web3, blockchain, and all the other things related to the NFT world. Some of us are trying to make a living out of it, even though the ones who are closest to us don't believe in us. 

We are here, and we will make it no matter what.
Don't ever wake up from this dream, as it's already becoming real!
